rComments: Professor Laroche clearly cares about his students and is passionate about what he does. He is very kind, understanding and hilarious. I would take this course a million times over if I could!

Professor Laroche's class is super amazing. He will teach you everything about Jazz Music, and you may have a chance to sing in his class. The grading system is super easy: complete quizzes and you're good to go. Read all his materials and try to sing it by yourself, then you will definitely get an A+.

Highly recommend this professor!!!
